Dear Hiring Team,

It is with great pleasure that I submit my candidacy for the Full-Stack Software Engineer role on the AI team with Aircall. I bring over three years of experience delivering full-stack systems with React, Python, AWS, and AI orchestration, plus a Master of Science in Computer Science from Pace University.

