Aircall's mission to empower professionals to have richer conversations through a cloud-based voice solution strongly resonates with me. I am especially aligned with your focus on Obsess Over Our Customers and Innovate & Iterate, and I would value the opportunity to help advance that mission through reliable, secure AI-powered product delivery. I would love to discuss this role further and can be reached at #ph or #eml.

